query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('admin',
'apache-poi',
'arguments',
'bootstrap-4',
'image-processing',
'jaxb',
'legend',
'nested',
'nsstring',
'qt4',
'spring-data',
'ssl');
